{"type": "article", "id": 27809, "title": "竹制家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-06T06:57:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151930Y16Uibw7XHqpfCPG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>和树木漫长的生长期相比，竹子成熟所需要的时间要来得更短，是一种具有可持续性的环保的材质。来自俄罗斯的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/alice_minkina\">Alice Minkina</a> 最近就以日本的嵯峨野竹林为名，推出了 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/26909913/Sagano-bamboo-furniture\">Sagano Bamboo</a> 家具系列，其中包括椅子以及配套的灯具和桌子。为了完成这套家具，Minkina 总共使用了 160 米长的削成条状的竹子，盘成圆盘后根据人体工学做出扭曲造型。虽然完成后很难看出竹子本身的样子，但竹子的坚韧性和天然的质感使家具拥有了一种不同的美感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151927yLr3CsoNaDfHgnqt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151928LGJzkAuCoVUispNY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021519293Jmc2oiAt1qlf50e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021519290eZN7EhJquFv69Um.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}